 scales,\nespecially during intense geomagnetic storms in which O$^+$ ions can dominate\nthe plasma composition in the inner magnetosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Apr 2021 00:31:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
