 adapted to individual\napplication cases by extending the network structure, it can be a general\nmethod by which practical systems can be built.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Apr 2021 08:22:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Jul 2021 06:44:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-27"}
